      "name": "PIV velocity field comparison at 3 L/min, 2500 RPM",
      "description": "Comparison of CFD-predicted velocity magnitudes against particle image velocimetry (PIV) measurements in the impeller region. Normalized RMS error of 4.2% across 1200 measurement points meets the MRL 2 acceptance threshold of less than 10%.",
      "prov:wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/synth/data/cpb-piv-validation-dataset"
