      "rationale": "Three meshes (4M, 8M, 16M hexahedral elements) evaluated at 3 L/min, 2500 RPM. Richardson extrapolation yields GCI of 1.8% for RH. Discretization error is within the MRL 2 acceptance threshold. The 8M mesh selected for production runs."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
