      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions match CFD inlet/outlet conditions within ±5%; blood analog fluid properties documented.",
      "rationale": "In-vitro tests used porcine blood at 37°C with hematocrit 35±2%. CFD boundary conditions set from measured flow rates and pressure heads. Fluid viscosity characterized by cone-and-plate rheometry. Temperature deviation between bench and simulation less than 0.5°C."
    },
