    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model adequately predicts hemolysis-relevant flow features within acceptance criteria. The model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB COU. RH < 1 acceptance criterion is achievable with demonstrated model accuracy.",
